lead_paragraph: The Nigerian men's soccer team didn't show any fatigue from a last-minute trip that brought the players to Brazil just hours before their Rio Olympics opener, beating Japan 5-4 Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: From Plane to Pitch, Nigeria Soccer Team Wins Olympic Opener
